  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening Social Cohesion and Resilience of Communities Affected by the Ituri Patriotic Resistance Force (FRPI)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following the signature of a peace agreement between the Congolese government and the Ituri Patriotic Resistance Force (FRPI) on February 28, 2020, the project seeks to contribute to the sustainable socio-economic reintegration of ex-combatants by promoting social cohesion in conflict-affected areas as well as adopting an approach benefitting local communities and promoting economic recovery.</narrative>
  </description>
